{"tid":680452,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一見到啲死利狗係到唱YNWA就想嘔","createTime":"2018-05-27T07:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T22:43:56.000Z","uid":3586,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb5aaef7bf482239617418a52fb7afc68c60cef","tid":680452,"uid":3586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"Henderson: &quot;It is not the mistakes Loris Karius made, we got to the final as a team and lose as a team. It is about everybody.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/155319_73d5a87f9d240b91c8b628642c56e413.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F155319_73d5a87f9d240b91c8b628642c56e413.png&h=ab4f6fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/155329_1dd2e19addebd6f70fb1d7367a2c537d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F155329_1dd2e19addebd6f70fb1d7367a2c537d.png&h=e04d2717&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/155340_182e5a4c6755f6c2df7073d11cf66aab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F155340_182e5a4c6755f6c2df7073d11cf66aab.png&h=5b5ce753&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/155348_b05f8d7baa79b49794bb826d83866eba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F155348_b05f8d7baa79b49794bb826d83866eba.png&h=6bdabce6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/155358_c1740af85db5c7670c30d1ac8cbd9e9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F155358_c1740af85db5c7670c30d1ac8cbd9e9b.png&h=ef71dcf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/155407_fed847f706d9a534b1bfe84addcd96bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F155407_fed847f706d9a534b1bfe84addcd96bb.png&h=707048fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/155435_a649a49092dd6801b0a8536dc0865509.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F155435_a649a49092dd6801b0a8536dc0865509.png&h=57ef38eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【軒達臣大方承認對手較佳】<br />\n<br />\n隊長軒達臣認為皇馬是表現較好的一隊，取勝合理。而紅軍則要向前看，迎接新球季來臨。<br />\n<br />\n「這當然很失望，我們曾經追成平手，重新返回正軌，但接著我們犯了數個錯誤，而皇馬表現又很好。我們都知道他們實力很強，也值得取勝，他們今晚表現明顯更佳。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們在30分鐘前表現出色，我們控球在腳，也能創造機會。但當沙拉受傷後，他們開始能夠保持控球，我們能半場賽和 0-0 也表現不錯。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們沒有放棄比賽，追回一球，但他們射入了其他晚上不會發生的失球。」<span style=\"color: red;\">對於卡列斯的犯錯：「其實我也不知道首球失球如何發生，第二球的倒掛他沒有事情可以挽救，第三球皮球有點飄。這不是要責怪他或那些錯誤，我們是一支球隊。我對所有球員感到自豪，我們以後要打入更多決賽。新球季即將開始，我們要快點向前看。」</span><br />\n<br />\n「我們被一支優秀的球隊打敗，傷口會痛一陣子。我們經歷了一個出色表現球季，以後要在英超和歐聯保持這個勢頭。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/tearful-jordan-henderson-loris-karius-14711432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liverpoolecho.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Ffootball-news%2Ftearful-jordan-henderson-loris-karius-14711432&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2FjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4aee3af8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/tearful-jordan-henderson-loris-karius-14711432</a>"},{"pid":"cee148f4f62a3cc3421d5277f2aec78c380f4ad5","tid":680452,"uid":42409,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:01:06.000Z","msg":"如果隊友都唔撐隊友想像唔到隊波會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過球迷永遠都係由自己角度出發睇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1553a159ace538cd25782d0804de7731c0cc12","tid":